 work. You take initiative on&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;projects and have a strong preference to be a trailblazer. Or when the &quot;trail&quot; is&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;given to you, you are motivated to challenge it and ensure it&#39;s the best trail every&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;step of the way.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;• You’re ready to roll up your sleeves for the team, and no task is beneath&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;you. Sometimes the work isn’t always sexy, but you’re down to do it anyway if it&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;means advancing the mission and providing value to our customers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;• You want to level up your software engineering skills. The power of Nira&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;comes from codifying our
